evidence.text: Plaintiff Mayor and City Council of Baltimore, Maryland (“Baltimore”) is a municipal corporation, organized pursuant to Articles XI and XI-A of the Maryland Constitution, entrusted with all the powers of local self-government and home rule afforded by those articles. Baltimore is the largest city in Maryland and the thirteenth largest city in the United States.
